r\" title=\"Kingdom of Sarnor\">Sarnor</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Shadow_Lands\" title=\"Shadow Lands\">Shadow Lands</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Land_of_the_Shrykes\" title=\"Land of the Shrykes\">Shrykes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Slaver%27s_Bay\" title=\"Slaver&#39;s Bay\">Slaver's Bay</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Valyrian_peninsula\" title=\"Valyrian peninsula\">Valyria</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Yi_Ti\" title=\"Yi Ti\">Yi Ti</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Sothoryos\" title=\"Sothoryos\">Sothoryos</a></td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Basilisk_Point\" title=\"Basilisk Point\">Basilisk Point</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Basilisk_Isles\" title=\"Basilisk Isles\">Basilisk Isles</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Green_Hell\" title=\"Green Hell\">Green Hell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Naath\" title=\"Naath\">Naath</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wyvern_Point\" title=\"Wyvern Point\">Wyvern Point</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Other</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Great_Moraq\" title=\"Great Moraq\">Great Moraq</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jade_Sea\" title=\"Jade Sea\">Jade Sea</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ibben\" title=\"Ibben\">Ibben</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Stepstones\" title=\"Stepstones\">Stepstones</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Isles\" title=\"Summer Isles\">Summer Isles</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Ulthos</a><